ygData.subject: Special Edition of EQ Presented by Wizard Cinema
ygData.msgSnippet: Wizard Cinema is proud to present the Special Edition of EQ on there weekly - daily newletter. Currently we have cancelled the newletter but it should run back
ygData.messageBody:
Wizard Cinema is proud to present the Special Edition of EQ on there weekly - daily newletter. Currently we have cancelled the newletter but it should run back up by Friday 12 of April 2002. After our manager's recent visit to Germany we had to delay the issue. (He must approve it) To join this maling list simply send your e-mail address to rmstci@... and you will be e-mailed by Wizard Cinema on how to join this maling list. It's been pretty sucessful. Currently we are un-able to let you join it throught the website and that is why you must e-mail it to rmstci@... We are experiencing technical difficulties with www.destined.to/wizfilm Please try not to go to the site as we are not sure what type of bugs are raiding it and may affect your computer's hard drives. If it does please note this e-mail to rmstci@... labling the subject as "To the Technical Support Department" Thank You - Wizard Cinema

Manager: "Anyone wishing to join please send all addresses to rmstci@... . I do advertise this live on EverQuest. My name on EQ is Ziward and I am a Dark Elf Wizard. Send me a tell or send me your name and I can hook up with you for fun questing. I do need help with the Tower of Spurned quest. The onme that the gentleman in red gives you in the Tower of the PSurned in Neriak COmmons. If you can help me please send all e-mails to rmstci@... titled "EQTOSQH" so It goes to the right department. Thank you! Good Hunting!"

This e-mail brought to you by Yahoo! Do you Yahoo? And also Wizard Cinema!
